<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="20" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,151,410]" pageId="4" pageNumber="20">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,322,151,177]" pageId="4" pageNumber="20">Remarks.</emphasis>
The female is here newly described. The male genitalia of the 
<typeStatus box="[1101,1208,152,178]" pageId="4" pageNumber="20">holotype</typeStatus>
slide (
